#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.103"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.103:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: sambodhivaggo (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "an3.103:0.2"
msgid "11. Sambodhavagga "
msgstr "11. Awakening "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.103:0.3"
msgid "103. Pubbevasambodhasutta "
msgstr "103. Before Awakening "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.259, sc1
msgctxt "an3.103:1.1"
msgid "“Pubbeva me, bhikkhave, sambodhā anabhisambuddhassa bodhisattasseva sato etadahosi: "
msgstr "“Mendicants, before my awakening—when I was still unawakened but intent on awakening—I thought: "

msgctxt "an3.103:1.2"
msgid "‘ko nu kho loke assādo, ko ādīnavo, kiṃ nissaraṇan’ti? "
msgstr "‘What’s the gratification in the world? What’s the drawback? What’s the escape?’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.103:1.3"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then it occurred to me: "

#. VAR: lokaṃ → loke (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.103:1.4"
msgid "‘yaṃ kho lokaṃ paṭicca uppajjati sukhaṃ somanassaṃ, ayaṃ loke assādo. "
msgstr "‘The pleasure and happiness that arise from the world: this is its gratification. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: loko → loke (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an3.103:1.5"
msgid "Yaṃ loko anicco dukkho vipariṇāmadhammo, ayaṃ loke ādīnavo. "
msgstr "That the world is impermanent, suffering, and perishable: this is its drawback. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: loke nissaraṇan’ti → lokanissaraṇaṃ (aṭṭha.)
msgctxt "an3.103:1.6"
msgid "Yo loke chandarāgavinayo chandarāgappahānaṃ, idaṃ loke nissaraṇan’ti. "
msgstr "Removing and giving up desire and greed for the world: this is its escape.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: abhisambuddho’ti → abhisambuddho (bj, s1-3, km, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an3.103:1.7"
msgid "Yāvakīvañcāhaṃ, bhikkhave, evaṃ lokassa assādañca assādato ādīnavañca ādīnavato nissaraṇañca nissaraṇato yathābhūtaṃ nābbhaññāsiṃ, neva tāvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya ‘anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ti paccaññāsiṃ. "
msgstr "As long as I didn’t truly understand the world’s gratification, drawback, and escape in this way for what they are, I didn’t announce my supreme perfect awakening in this world with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: khvāhaṃ → kho ahaṃ (bj, pts1) | khohaṃ (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "an3.103:1.8"
msgid "Yato ca khvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, evaṃ lokassa assādañca assādato ādīnavañca ādīnavato nissaraṇañca nissaraṇato yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ, athāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya ‘anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ti paccaññāsiṃ. "
msgstr "But when I did truly understand the world’s gratification, drawback, and escape in this way for what they are, I announced my supreme perfect awakening in this world with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.103:1.9"
msgid "Ñāṇañca pana me dassanaṃ udapādi: "
msgstr "Knowledge and vision arose in me: "

#. VAR: vimutti → cetovimutti (bj, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an3.103:1.10"
msgid "‘akuppā me vimutti, ayamantimā jāti, natthi dāni punabbhavo’”ti. "
msgstr "‘My freedom is unshakable; this is my last rebirth; now there are no more future lives.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.103:1.11"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

